nom.bdezonia.zorbage.sampling

Class SamplingCylindricalRealGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • nom.bdezonia.zorbage.sampling.SamplingCylindricalRealGrid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Set<RealIndex>, Sampling<RealIndex>, DimensionCount

    public class SamplingCylindricalRealGrid
extends java.lang.Object
implements Sampling<RealIndex>
    SamplingCylindricalGrid is a 3-d Sampling in real cylindrical space. It defines the grid origin's r, z, and theta coordinates plus spacings and counts. This allows one to build cylindrical coordinate grids that are partially complete if so desired. .
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
